sectionText: Students in the online CL course  must also register for the online CQ discussion section.  Video lectures, course materials, and a discussion board will be made available online through Compass2g.  Optional face-to-face Supplementary Instruction sessions will also be available to all students.  Students are expected to complete online assignments as outlined in the course syllabus.  This section has one or more proctored exams which will be administered in-person; an online option for taking exams is available and may carry additional fees.
